NordVPN Selective Routing for pfSense allows per-device and per-VLAN
policy-based routing through NordVPN, with support for multiple
simultaneous tunnels managed entirely through the pfSense GUI.

Features:
- Route specific VLANs, subnets, or individual IPs through NordVPN
- Multiple simultaneous tunnels (different servers per device/VLAN)
- Easy server switching per tunnel without disrupting other tunnels
- Kill switch to block non-VPN traffic if a tunnel drops
- DNS leak prevention with configurable DNS modes
- Fully integrated into the pfSense VPN menu
